# committed repo docs/config, drop the line and `git add` them.)
/.codex/
/.mcp.json
/AGENTS.md
/Build/
/package-lock.json
/Tools/Generated/
/Tools/_gen_tex/
/Tools/_laser_audit/
# Pak crypto/signing config -- per-environment, may carry keys; never commit (secret-safe).
/Config/DefaultCrypto.ini
